data.description: Just built KB home in the WildHawk Community at Roberts Ranch. NO HOA. Large One Story Home, Corner Lot with Latest Energy Star Certified Features throughout Home and Garage. This Spacious home offers a Convenient, Designated Work/Study Area off Kitchen and Great Room! Home has barely been lived in. Kitchen never used. Upgrades include Upgraded Granite Countertops, Ceiling fans, All New Window Coverings, Builder's Pantry, Solar, Water Efficient Landscaping, Electric Vehicle Charging Station, Garage door Opener, Upgraded Covered Patio, Tankless Water Heater, Whole House Fan, Ring, Soaker Tub and Shower, 10 Year Builder Warranty in Place and Conveniently Located Close to Highway 80 and 505 while near Travis AFB, Kaiser, North Bay Vaca Valley Hospital, UC Davis and Sacramento. Dining, Schools and Parks are Nearby.
